Taking a breather from the daily rush, I escaped to the serene comfort of Fortune Sullivan Court, Ooty — a staycation that blended timeless charm with heartfelt hospitality. 🌿✨

Tucked away in the hills, this colonial-style property instantly makes you slow down and soak in the calm. From the warm wooden interiors and mountain views to the comforting flavors of local cuisine, every element here whispers ease and elegance.

Whether it was sipping hot chai in the garden, strolling through mist-kissed mornings, or simply enjoying the cozy corners perfect for unwinding (and yes, creating content too!), this stay felt like a hug from the hills. 🏔️☕🛏️

If you’re looking for a soulful escape that’s equal parts restful and refined, @fortuneresortsullivancourtooty is that hidden gem in Ooty you didn’t know you needed. A big thank you to the entire team for making it such a memorable experience. ❤️🌼

latestPosts.caption:
🌄 Doddabetta Peak Itinerary – a must visit spot in Ooty ⛰️

Save this for your next Ooty trip 🧭✨

🌲Enterance fee: ₹10
🌲Extra charges for Still & Video Cameras

➡️Doddabetta, 2,637 metres, is the highest peak in the Nilgiris and the third-highest in South India. Located just 9 km from Ooty and @fortuneresortsullivancourtooty , it’s a popular tourist spot with road access and scenic forest views.

📍 Start Early – Reach by 7–8 AM to catch the misty sunrise & avoid the crowd.
🚶‍♀️ Mini Trek to the Top – Short but worth it! Scenic views all the way up.
📸 Photo Stop – Capture panoramic Nilgiri Hills from the telescope house.
☕ Quick Bite – Try local tea & snacks from stalls nearby.
🛍️ Explore Nearby – Visit Tea Museum or Botanical Garden on your way back.

🔁 Tag your travel partner & plan your mountain escape!
📌 Save this post for your next Ooty adventure!
